{"uuid":"recommended222604","createDate":1568394120000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"222604\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:23:04\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2019-09-14\",\"gameName\":\"Train Simulator: Southern Pacific SD70M Loco\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/222604\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/222604/\",\"playTime\":\"0.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2019-09-14\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"0.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/222604\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Train Simulator: Southern Pacific SD70M Loco","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 模拟火车: Southern Pacific SD70M 机车组\n <br>\n 包含了SD70M机车组~车头模拟包含了汽笛、铃声、车灯、室内灯光、仪表灯开关等~\n <br>\n 不过刹车节流阀是一体的~毕竟货运车~慢死了~\n <br>\n 还有个掰了会自动归位的诡异刹车（什么鬼~我是不会去看手册为啥这样的）~\n <br>\n 总的来说~车头很高~视野很开阔~似乎大多美国车的车头都超高的~\n <br>\n <br>\n 如果你有Sherman Hill Route线路~会发现到有一个职业任务~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/208286/Train_Simulator_Sherman_Hill_Route_AddOn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/208286/Train_Simulator_Sherman_Hill_Route_AddOn/</a>\n <br>\n 而且职业任务是运悍马坦克的~好长一排~而且超远距离运输~emm~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1862570241\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1862570241</a>\n <br>\n 可惜速度慢死了~不过好处是闯红灯不会直接game over~\n <br>\n <div class=\"bb_h1\">\n  可惜一路都是美国荒野~+限速极低~以及那诡异抽搐的刹车~\n </div>\n <br>\n 当然~似乎还有其他线路会有其他职业任务~我只有那条线路~一个职业任务~\n</div>\n<div id=\"ReviewEdit\" style=\"display: none\">\n <textarea id=\"ReviewEditTextArea\" class=\"review_edit_text_area\" maxlength=\"8000\" rows=\"2\" cols=\"80\">模拟火车: Southern Pacific SD70M 机车组\n包含了SD70M机车组~车头模拟包含了汽笛、铃声、车灯、室内灯光、仪表灯开关等~\n不过刹车节流阀是一体的~毕竟货运车~慢死了~\n还有个掰了会自动归位的诡异刹车（什么鬼~我是不会去看手册为啥这样的）~\n总的来说~车头很高~视野很开阔~似乎大多美国车的车头都超高的~\n\n如果你有Sherman Hill Route线路~会发现到有一个职业任务~\nhttps://store.steampowered.com/app/208286/Train_Simulator_Sherman_Hill_Route_AddOn/\n而且职业任务是运悍马坦克的~好长一排~而且超远距离运输~emm~\nhttps://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1862570241\n可惜速度慢死了~不过好处是闯红灯不会直接game over~\n[h1]可惜一路都是美国荒野~+限速极低~以及那诡异抽搐的刹车~[/h1]\n\n当然~似乎还有其他线路会有其他职业任务~我只有那条线路~一个职业任务~</textarea>\n <div class=\"review_edit_received_compensation\">\n  <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\" value=\"1\"> <label for=\"ReceivedCompensationCheckbox\">如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框 <a data-tooltip-text=\"如果您是免费获取的此产品，请勾选此框。您的评测旁会显示“免费获取的产品”。如果您评测此游戏还收到了其他报酬，必须在您的评测文本中披露。\">(?)</a></label>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: left\">\n  您推荐这款游戏吗？ <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover active\" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingPositive();\" id=\"OwnerVoteUpBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_up\"></i> 是</span> </span> <span class=\"btnv6_blue_hoverfade btn_small_thin ico_hover \" onclick=\"SetOwnerRatingNegative();\" id=\"OwnerVoteDownBtn\"> <span><i class=\"ico16 thumb_down\"></i>否</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"float: right\">\n  <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_grey_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"CancelEdits();\" id=\"CancelEditsBtn\"> <span>取消</span> </span> <span class=\"btn_small_thin btn_blue_white_innerfade\" onclick=\"SaveReview();\" id=\"SaveReviewBtn\"> <span>保存修改</span> </span>\n </div>\n <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</div>","bgArchivesType":{"uuid":"d612b8f8-70ee-4b73-9f32-04475fbe954e","code":"Steam游戏评测","name":"Steam游戏评测","parentUuid":"a4fb2b94-3d2b-414d-8745-49677c3c7d22"}}